description: GSMA Mobile Money Metrics is an interactive tool that provides a comprehensive set of global metrics for the industry by combining unique data sources that the GSMA Mobile Money programme has been collecting and analysing since its inception. Mobile Money Metrics is designed to support the efforts of mobile money providers and the wider international development community to deliver on the ambition of achieving greater financial inclusion, financial empowerment and economic growth.
